    "notes": "Cooling Schedule\n\n**Please check chemical stock levels and raise an action if required**\n\nQuarterly tower LP samples have to be taken in 1 Litre bottle - Suite LP FILTERED\n\nNB H4255 INHIBITOR: Can test for Molybdate (5ppm-8ppm) or Phosphonate (Product Factor = 16 to get 200-300ppm total)\n\nInhibitor = WTP H4255 Phosphonate (Multiply no. of drops by 16, target is 200-300mg/l)\n\nJan-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nFeb-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nMar-- Q- 6pts - Onsite chemical monitoring, 2 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from softened feed  and evaporative cooling system, 1 x LP from evaporative cooling system. Tower inspection included\n\nApr-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nMay-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nJun-- Q- 6pts - Onsite chemical monitoring, 2 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from softened feed  and evaporative cooling system, 1 x LP from evaporative cooling system. Tower inspection included\n\nJul-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nAug-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nSep-- Q- 6pts - Onsite chemical monitoring, 2 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from softened feed  and evaporative cooling system, 1 x LP from evaporative cooling system. Tower inspection included\n\nOct-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nNov-M- 4pts -Onsite chemical monitoring, 1 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from evaporative cooling system.\n\nDec - Q- 6pts - Onsite chemical monitoring, 2 x TVC (Suite = COOLING) from softened feed  and evaporative cooling system, 1 x LP from evaporative cooling system. Tower inspection included",
